msg: Added FallbackFacetFactory to bring together all defaults, is registered in DefaultFacetFactorySet; also renamed some other facets that didn't have *Facet suffix; also renamed LifecycleFacet -> CallbackFacet

author: dkhaywood
msg: FacetFactory and Facet reworked - the featureTypes now belong to FacetFactory rather than Facet; this means that FacetFactorySet can now return all factories for a given NakedObjectFeatureType.
